<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="icon" href="img/icons/logo.png" type="image/icon">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/facilities.css">
    <title>Facilities</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('templates/header-1.ejs') -%>
        <div class="topImage">
            <span class="topImageTitle">Facilities</span>
        </div>
        <div class="custom-container">
            <div class="custom-container-section">
                <div class="section-description">
                    The placement office is fully equipped to efficiently support all stages of the recruitment procedure. Our staff will handle all arrangements for interviews, group discussions, and pre-placement talks. We have various well-equipped facilities to facilitate these processes, including:
                </div>
            </div>
          
            <div class="grid-container">
                <div class="grid-child purple" style="padding-inline-start:5%;">
                    <div class="prog">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary my-btn active" id="btn-1" style="color:black;font-size:1.2rem; font-family: Inter;
                        font-style: normal;">Smart class-rooms</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary my-btn" id="btn-2" style="color:black;font-size:1.2rem; font-family: Inter;
                        font-style: normal;">Interview rooms and Group discussions halls</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary my-btn" id="btn-3" style="color:black;font-size:1.2rem; font-family: Inter;
                        font-style: normal;">Computer labs</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary my-btn" id="btn-4" style="color:black;font-size:1.2rem; font-family: Inter;
                        font-style: normal;">Student placement volunteers</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary my-btn" id="btn-5" style="color:black;font-size:1.2rem; font-family: Inter;
                        font-style: normal;">Video conferencing facilities</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-child green" style="padding-top: 1.5rem; padding-right:10%;">
                    <div class="custom-container-section">
                        <div class="section-box" id="box-1" style="display: flex; border-radius: 3%;">
                            <div>
                                <img class="section-box-item section-custom-img" style=" border-radius: 10%; overflow:hidden;"
                                    src="img/projector.JPG"
                                    alt="office">
                            </div>
                            <div class="section-box-item section-custom-para">
                                <h2>Smart class-rooms</h2>
                                <p style="color:black;font-size:1.35rem; font-family: Inter;font-style: normal;">Our smart lecture halls come with the best technology and provide a conducive
                                    atmosphere
                                    for
                                    dynamic and focused discussions between the speakers and the audience.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="custom-container-section">
                        <div class="section-box" id="box-2" style="display: none; border-radius: 3%;">
                            <div class="section-box-item section-custom-para2">
                                <h2>Interview rooms and Group discussions halls</h2>
                                <p style="color:black;font-size:1.35rem; font-family: Inter;font-style: normal;">A very minimalistic yet expansive looking space for conducting interviews, group
                                    discussions,
                                    pre-placement talks etc.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <img class="section-box-item section-custom-img" style="border-radius: 10%;"
                                src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1fHFQJdTKe9BqJBvRVioHwn9j24sJUWoS" alt="room"
                                srcset="">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="custom-container-section">
                        <div class="section-box " id="box-3" style="display: none; border-radius: 3%;">
                            <img class="section-box-item section-custom-img"  style="  border-radius: 10%;" src="/img/facilities/computer_lab.jpg"
                                alt="office">
                            <div class="section-box-item section-custom-para">
                                <h2>Computer labs</h2>
                                <p style="color:black;font-size:1.35rem; font-family: Inter;font-style: normal;">The college has high-tech all-in-one computer systems enabled with extremely fast
                                    internet access
                                    through LAN and WiFi (>100 Mbps). These systems are equipped with the cutting edge
                                    hardware
                                    configurations and are connected to a central server.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="custom-container-section">
                        <div class="section-box" id="box-4" style="display: none; border-radius: 3%;">
                            <div class="section-box-item section-custom-para1">
                                <h2>Student placement volunteers</h2>
                                <p style="color:black;font-size:1.35rem; font-family: Inter;font-style: normal;">Student placement volunteers to assist on the day of visit and through the selection
                                    process</p>
                            </div>
                            <img class="section-box-item section-custom-img"  style="  border-radius: 10%;"
                                src="img/volunteers.png"
                                alt="volunteers" srcset="">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="custom-container-section">
                        <div class="section-box" id="box-5" style="display: none; border-radius: 3%;">
                            <img class="section-box-item section-custom-img"  style="  border-radius: 10%;"
                                src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=18-xphkMSE6ARRNJR5k91wAjLt01xTN9l"
                                alt="office">
                            <div class="section-box-item section-custom-para">
                                <h2>Video conferencing facilities</h2>
                                <p></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <script src="scripts/facilities.js"></script>
            </div>
           

                <%- include('templates/footer-1.ejs') -%>
</body>

</html>
